  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/494b89c4a070774fd1f2edb305548e84.poster.avif?t=1610999781\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/494b89c4a070774fd1f2edb305548e84.webm?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/494b89c4a070774fd1f2edb305548e84.mp4?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fate’s Call: A New Beginning embark in an epic VR Fantasy RPG !</strong><br><br>You are Talos, a hero that has been awoken by ancient ghosts to save it's world once again.<br>Evil forces are plotting against peace. <br>You are the only one who can stop them. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/382e4009f02d7d12cf3c42e76f2a3765.webp?t=1610999781\" width=547 height=47 /></span><br><br>Fully voiced story, travel across the world of Fates Call ! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/330f91b4770fd0359214f5dcdd48d605.poster.avif?t=1610999781\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/330f91b4770fd0359214f5dcdd48d605.webm?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/330f91b4770fd0359214f5dcdd48d605.mp4?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/54f567877fee1185bda3d9008e8be946.webp?t=1610999781\" width=547 height=47 /></span><br>Explore the vast lands, delve into it's dark dungeons, and travel across the open seas.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/0d625c7ef63af78599eb673c7a836115.poster.avif?t=1610999781\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/0d625c7ef63af78599eb673c7a836115.webm?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/0d625c7ef63af78599eb673c7a836115.mp4?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/623006a59d2558a24dd0425e741aec1f.webp?t=1610999781\" width=547 height=47 /></span><br><br>Battle hordes of enemies and bosses as you progress in Fates Call story.<br><br><strong>Parry their attacks and find an opening to cut them to pieces ! </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/16e5439972a75e8bf46a54230bda7c91.poster.avif?t=1610999781\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/16e5439972a75e8bf46a54230bda7c91.webm?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/16e5439972a75e8bf46a54230bda7c91.mp4?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Annihilate them with powerful spells </strong> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/adbd60f421dbc7ea180c1778484bf506.poster.avif?t=1610999781\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/adbd60f421dbc7ea180c1778484bf506.webm?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/adbd60f421dbc7ea180c1778484bf506.mp4?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Or follow the path of the ranger, and fill your enemies with arrows </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/10b2f1af4d99c90c7dd87432446f5b5f.poster.avif?t=1610999781\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/10b2f1af4d99c90c7dd87432446f5b5f.webm?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/10b2f1af4d99c90c7dd87432446f5b5f.mp4?t=1610999781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/d1393aab644bd57f296eb3ac01875a90.webp?t=1610999781\" width=547 height=47 /></span><br><br>You'll meet several companions, each of them has unique gameplay and will help you during your journey ! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691090/extras/48f6c245d1e3fc7ff4d01cb14efbe6b8.avif?t=1610999781\" width=547 height=200 /></span><br><br>Compatible Headset & Controllers : Vive, Index, Oculus, Window Mixed Reality<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steams